rows.label: qev085901_MSG0001
rows.name:
Hey, look who's here!
Thanks again for the help last time.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085901_MSG0002
rows.name: Hmm? When did you work with Elma's team?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085901_MSG0003
rows.name:
Uh, when a certain someone decided to
just wander off and leave us high and dry![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085901_MSG0004
rows.name: Oh yeah? Well, I hope whoever it was got chewed out good.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085901_MSG0005
rows.name:
Looks like I owe you one, Elma.
Order something if you like, my treat.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085901_MSG0006
rows.name: REALLY?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085901_MSG0007
rows.name:
Ohhh...Tatsu filled to bursting with food and joy...
Lao is good and generous friend.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085901_MSG0008
rows.name: You tubby little... I said order SOMETHING, not EVERYTHING.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085901_MSG0009
rows.name: It's okay, Lao. Next meal, it'll be Tatsu's turn...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085901_MSG0010
rows.name: So, Shingo...you gonna say something?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085901_MSG0011
rows.name:
Go ahead and ask. I'm sure these ladies
will give you better advice than I can.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085901_MSG0012
rows.name: Having trouble with something?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085901_MSG0013
rows.name: Oh, er, I... It's not...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085901_MSG0014
rows.name: Ooh! I know![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085901_MSG0014_2
rows.name: Shingo has a cruuuuush on someoooone![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085901_MSG0015
rows.name: W-wait, WHAT?! How'd you know?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085901_MSG0016
rows.name: Oh, come on. Seriously?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085901_JNK0010
rows.name: Grin

rows.label: qev085901_SEL0011
rows.name: Say it's written all over his face.

rows.label: qev085901_JNK0020
rows.name: Shrug

rows.label: qev085901_SEL0021
rows.name: Say you had no idea.

rows.label: qev085901_MSG0017
rows.name: I know, right? He's a total open book.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085901_MSG0018
rows.name: I get that a lot...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085901_MSG0019
rows.name: Oh my gosh, it's totally obvious! How do you not see it?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085901_MSG0020
rows.name: I get that a lot...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085901_MSG0021
rows.name:
If you're done making the poor man sweat,
why don't you hear him out?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085901_MSG0022
rows.name:
But look, if this is about winning a girl's heart,
Lao is the probably the guy you wanna ask.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085901_MSG0023
rows.name:
He knows you a lot better than we do
since you work together and all.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085901_MSG0024
rows.name: Plus he was married, so he can—[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085901_MSG0025
rows.name: Sorry, Shingo, I should get going.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085901_MSG0026
rows.name: Er, right. Of course, sir.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085901_MSG0027
rows.name: Good luck. I'll keep my fingers crossed.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085901_MSG0028
rows.name: Th-thank you, sir.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085901_MSG0029
rows.name: Um, yeah. We don't really talk about Lao's family.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085901_MSG0030
rows.name: Oh my gosh, I didn't mean—[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085901_JNK0030
rows.name: Comfort

rows.label: qev085901_SEL0031
rows.name: Tell her not to worry about it.

rows.label: qev085901_JNK0040
rows.name: Cheer

rows.label: qev085901_SEL0041
rows.name: Try to make her smile.

rows.label: qev085901_MSG0031
rows.name: Thanks. I still feel like a total oaf, though... Ugh.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085901_MSG0032
rows.name: Yeah, I don't really feel like smiling at the moment...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085901_MSG0033
rows.name: He wasn't angry, Lin. You heard him wish Shingo luck.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085901_MSG0034
rows.name: Yes yes! Angry Lao not talk like that.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085901_MSG0035
rows.name: Thanks, guys.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085901_MSG0036
rows.name:
Yeah, so, if you don't mind,
I really do need some advice on this.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085901_MSG0037
rows.name: I'm at the end of my rope.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085901_MSG0038
rows.name: Sure. Whatever we can do to help.[ST:wait ]
